    统计和生成所有不同的二叉树

    vuePress-theme-reco AuraroJ    2022

    统计和生成所有不同的二叉树

    AuraroJ 2022/9/19 递归
    public List<<Node> generateTrees(int n){
    return generate(1, n);
}
public List<Node> generate(int st, int end) {
    List<Node> res = new ArrayList<>();
    if(st > end) res.add(null);
    Node head = null;
    for(int i = start; i <= end; i++) {
        head = new Node(i);
        List<Node> lsubs = generate(st, i - 1);
        List<Node> rsubs = generate(i + 1, end);
        for(Node l : lsubs) {
            for(Node r : rsubs) {
                head.left = l;
                head.right = r;
                res.add(cloneTree(head));
            }
        }
    }
    return res;
}
public Node cloneTree(Node head) {
    if(head == null) return null;
    Node res = new Node(head.value);
    res.left = cloneTree(head.left);
    res.right = cloneTree(head.right);
    return res;
}
